data.title: Nova Southeastern University Athletics
data.meta_description: The Nova Southeastern University Department of Athletics appreciates the efforts our student-athletes have put forth to help our program achieve athletic excellence.
data.text:
The Nova Southeastern University Department of Athletics appreciates the efforts our student-athletes have put forth to help our program achieve athletic excellence. As we continue to build toward future successes on the playing fields and in the classroom, Sharks Athletics would like to follow the career achievements and personal successes of our alumni base.

Athletic Alumni also have an opportunity to join the NSU Athletics Varsity Club, an initiative designed to provide former student-athletes, coaches and staff (Knights and Sharks) an avenue to sustain tradition, reconnect and support the future of NSU Athletics. For details click the button below.
